# {{.Type}}: {{.Name}}

`{{.Name}}` describes the configuration of a log integration at the project level. Supported integration types include AWS S3, Google Cloud Storage, Azure Blob Storage, Datadog, Splunk, and OpenTelemetry.

To use this data source, the requesting Service Account or API Key must have the Organization Owner or Project Owner role.

## Example Usage

```terraform
data "mongodbatlas_log_integration" "example" {
  project_id     = var.project_id
  integration_id = var.integration_id
}

output "integration_type" {
  value = data.mongodbatlas_log_integration.example.type
}
```

